sequenceDiagram
    participant Config
    participant API
    participant Parser as OpaqueNoParse
    participant Meta
    participant Time
    participant Env
    participant Exposure
    participant Handoff

    Config->>Config: Resolve opaque profile + OpaqueNoParse binding
    API->>Parser: Opaque content only
    Parser-->>Env: Opaque parsed content ref
    Meta-->>Env: Prepared metadata block
    Time-->>Env: Stabilized timestamp
    Env->>Exposure: Final envelope readiness
    Exposure->>Handoff: Ready exposure
